    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-string S54 straight-six power plant. This unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Technical highlights include a reinforced rear subframe, refreshed suspension bushings for optimal turn-in geometry, and a recently overhauled cooling system. This example represents a mechanically honest machine with the structural integrity and throttle response characteristic of BMW's finest naturally aspirated era.",
